item.title: Which iPhone is Bigger? Find Out the Surprising Answer!
item.description: Introduction When it comes to iPhones, there are a lot of different models available in the market. From the latest iPhones to the older models, there are a variety of sizes, features, and prices. But which iPhone is bigger? Is it the latest model or the older one? This is a question that many people have asked, and the answer may surprise you. iPhone 5s and iPhone SE The iPhone 5s and iPhone SE are two of the older models of iPhones available.
